Equities drifted further downwards on the BSE market Tuesday in
the wake of heavy bull liquidation and selling pressure from
foreign funds.
</P>
<P>
The sensitive index dropped to the intra-day low of 3540.61 at
the initial stages due to continued onslaught by bulls, who were
disappointed by the Union budget for 1998-99 presented to
Parliament Monday. 
