Monday, the striking pilots and the management will resume talks
Tuesday afternoon. The French Minister of Transport Jean-Claude
Gayssot has suggested modifying the legislative disposal on the
exchange between the stocks of Air France and a 15 percent
reduction of the salaries for the pilots. 
