<HEADLINE> Chinese President Meets U.S President's Security Assistant </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, June 2 (Xinhua) -- It has been demonstrated that a
sound and improving Sino-U.S. relationship is of great importance
not only to the people of both countries, but to the stability and
security of the world as a whole, President Jiang Zemin said here
today.
