nuclear tests to restore the strategic balance in the region and
deter aggression.
</P>
<P>
Pakistan was left with no option but to take appropriate steps
to offset the grave threat posed to its security by India's
nuclear tests and belligerent attitude on the Kashmir issue,
Sharif said while meeting visiting Iranian Foreign Minister Kamal
Kharazi, according to official sources.
</P>
