bilateral trade and further deepening of mutual economic links
between Pakistan and Iran.
</P>
<P>
In this regard, the need for the early finalization of an oil
refinery and a gas pipeline project was stressed.
</P>
<P>
During the meeting, the situation in Afghanistan was also
discussed in detail.
</P>
<P>
Sharif stressed the need for an early end to the Afghan
conflict and Pakistan's determination to work closely with Iran in
this regard.
</P>
<P>
The Iranian foreign minister affirmed his country's commitment
to a close Iran-Pakistan relationship as well as its readiness to
work together with Pakistan for an early end to the Afghan
conflict.
</P>
<P>
The two sides agreed to intensify their joint efforts for the
promotion of intra-Afghan dialogue and the acceleration of the
peace process.
