 "Xinhua Daily Telegraph"
</P>
<P>
-- Chinese President Jiang Zemin, during a meeting here
yesterday with visiting Turkish Deputy Prime Minister Bulent
Ecevit, expressed his appreciation of the positive attitude
adopted by the Turkish government towards the development of
Sino-Turkish relations.
</P>
<P>
-- On the International Children's Day, senior Chinese
officials Hu Jintao and Li Lanqing here yesterday met with
representatives of children and social workers on children and had
a photo taken with them.
</P>
<P>
Hu Jintao, Standing Committee member of the Political Bureau of
the Communist Party of China (CPC) Central Committee and
vice-president of China, extended warm regards to the children and
hard-working teachers across the country.
</P>
