<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, June 2 (Xinhua) -- Hong Kong's Secretary for
Information Technology and Broadcasting Kwong Ki-chi left here
Tuesday for Singapore to attend the third Asia Pacific Economic
Cooperation (APEC) Ministerial Meeting on Telecommunications and
Information.
</P>
<P>
